metadata.name: SUP
metadata.description:
Trying to practice **yoga on SUP** is a **challenge** itself, not to mention how distracted you may be when surrounded by **breathtaking** North European **landscape**.

This **100% hand drawn** original digital artwork was created with love to **yoga**, mother **nature**, and healthy lifestyle.

Every drawing from Yoga project contains a strict **list of must-have elements**, such as main hero, little animal friend etc. 

You can **read more** about all elements of Yoga project in this [Blog Article](https://www.catasian.net/post/elements-and-principles-of-yoga-project).

By **June 2023** there were created **12 original drawings** for **Yoga** art project by artist Zhenya Hitrova. 

Find out more about the artist on [Official Website](https://www.catasian.net/).
